Sender  Sidious~
Date    Wed Apr 24 00:47:38 2002~
Stamp   1019627258
To      all~
Subject PK Rules and Stuff~
Text
Dont even know why I have to remind some people only 2 days after
doing the new rules but I must.

Once you are in a clan you are ALWAYS in that clan. No matter what.
Only way out is deletion or the leader finds clear cut facts
on why you should be booted. And if you try to get booted on
purpose you get a nifty Traitor flag. So choose wisely.

Duels: Friendly duels are just that. No loot/sac. When you agree
to that you stick to it. You loot someone in a friendly duel you are slain.
So get used to actually living up to your own word and get some honor.

Have any problems with them come to me. But I stand firm on these.

Sidious
~
