To      all~
Subject Grand opening of Gunsmith Cats!~
Text
As some of you know by now, Gunsmith Cats has been opened.

This store deals in pistols, spare magazines, and ammunition. Pending a resolution
with local legislation and law enforcement, Rally will be carrying rifles and shotguns
in stock as well.

(Other stores will be opened as time passes, but many of these would be carrying
illegal weapons and thus won't announce their existence to the general public.)

Gunsmith Cats is located on 8th Avenue, just south of Downtown Square. The southern Neo
Tokyo map has been updated to reflect the store's location.

- Kevin.
~
